headline: Should You Reconsider A. O. Smith After Its Shares Fell 5% in the Past Month?
summary: Deciding what to do with A. O. Smith stock these days might feel like you are peering through a slightly foggy window. Recent price movements give us plenty to ponder. Over the last week, the stock slipped by 3.6%, extending a gradual slide of 5.2% for the past 30 days. At first glance, that could sound discouraging, but a broader look tells a more interesting story. If you have been holding since three years ago, you have seen a 40.5% total return, and even over five years, the stock is up...
